org.apache.lucene.codecs

Class UndeadNormsProducer

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.lucene.codecs.NormsProducer
      • org.apache.lucene.codecs.UndeadNormsProducer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Closeable, AutoCloseable, Accountable

    public class UndeadNormsProducer
extends NormsProducer
    Used only for backwards compatibility corner case, to provide re-animated norms when all fields are undead.
    NOTE: This API is for internal purposes only and might change in incompatible ways in the next release.
